Name: DominaTRIX - Hentai Storytelling Puzzle
About the game: DominaTRIX is a puzzle game with a unique story about a dominatrix working at a tavern full of minotaurs. Opposite to many other games of the genre, in this one each image doesn't seem to make sense individually but together they create a complete narrative. The Gallery has the complete scenes while the gameplay has a part of them. Enjoy both. Administrator Mode Keyboard F: Press it for a few seconds and complete the level Features Original Story mixed with sexual fetishes; A Powerful Furry Girl; 10 levels with high-quality art; Gallery; No censorship; Steam Achievements;
